# References layer

## Roles

| Path | Purpose |
|------|---------|
| `scan-checklist.md` | Phase 0 checkboxes |
| `SCAN-REPORT-SCHEMA.md` | Scan Report v2 shape |
| `*-FORMAT.md` | CONTEXT, AGENTS, emergency handoff shapes |
| `MDC-RULES-FORMAT.md` | Phase 2 `.mdc` write order, `proposed_mdc_rules`, activation patterns |
| `annexes/*.md` | Per-host **detection** paths — inventory only |
| `annexes/mcp.md` | MCP inventory; offer merge only on user request |
| `research/` | Forensics research (sanitized); cite when extending checklist |
| `question-bank.md` | Grill questions |
| `cursor-notes.md` | Cursor-only execution notes |
| `HOST-EXTENSION.md` | Maintainer add/remove host recipe |

## Editing annexes

- **Official docs first** (cursor.com, code.claude.com, developers.openai.com, etc.).
- Mark **verify locally** when Antigravity/Gemini paths conflict.
- Do not copy annex paragraphs into SKILL.md — link from checklist/INDEX instead.
- New host → follow [HOST-EXTENSION.md](../../references/HOST-EXTENSION.md) (annex + INDEX + checklist).

## CONTEXT / AGENTS philosophy (enforce in formats)

- **CONTEXT.md** (target repos): glossary only — no file trees, proof commands, or run-state.
- **AGENTS.md**: read order, boundaries, proof command, short stack gotchas.
- **Run-state** → emergency handoff or trim list in Scan Report — never CONTEXT.

## Cross-links

Keep relative links valid from `references/` and from repo root. After moves, grep for stale `brownfield-agent-init` or old project names.
